{
  "stem": "26142.12",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "All they wanted is 90 years to show that we lived in this place.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And it was more than 100, 120 years.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "My great grandfathers were in there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So-- but this was a way of squeezing out the last Jews.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "When I finally the-- the paper, they wanted to send it to Torun, officially.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "In Torun, we couldn't-- we couldn't go back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So my cousin in Mariapocs managed-- gave us an idea.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Debrecen, I found out-- I believe I mentioned that already, but I'll repeat it again, that my brother [NON-ENGLISH] was being brought over.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was saved, and sent to Satu Mare.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my father had-- father and mother had to leave Torun and become a refugee, and live in [NON-ENGLISH] with their-- with his sister, sister and brother-in-law.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Sometimes in-- in October or November, we got a notification from the lawyer that we can get-- we will get the citizenship paper.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My brother Eliezer was supposedly the legal one, because he was not deported on the other side.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He traveled to Budapest.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they insisted-- and they insisted that they can-- they have to send it registered to Torun.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They cannot give it to the lawyer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They cannot give it out to the per-- It has to go through-- registered to an office.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this was a big obstacle.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We couldn't go to Torun.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We knew that this is going into the lion's-- lion's den, or lion's mouth.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But my cousin in Mariapocs, he had an idea.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said, maybe if you convince the lawyer, he should convince the authorities in Budapest, that you are living now-- [NON-ENGLISH] was living already in Mariapocs.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then I come over to Mariapocs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they send it directly to the notary in there officially.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
